s in 2028.\", \"from\": 347, \"to\": 528, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 347, \"end\": 362, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999340616, \"rank\": 6.576239556190523e-11, \"text\": \"World Athletics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\"}, {\"begin\": 419, \"end\": 425, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monaco\", \"score\": 0.9999998358957917, \"rank\": 1.5817224070882125e-07, \"text\": \"Monaco\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monaco\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monaco\"}, {\"begin\": 499, \"end\": 519, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1984_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999758156267, \"rank\": 2.418440452876064e-08, \"text\": \"Los Angeles Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1984_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1984_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"track\", \"from\": 378, \"to\": 383}, {\"ngram\": \"field\", \"from\": 388, \"to\": 393}, {\"ngram\": \"its headquarters\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 415}, {\"ngram\": \"prize money\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 460}, {\"ngram\": \"silver and bronze medalists\", \"from\": 464, \"to\": 491}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement \\\"It is important we start somewhere and make sure some of the revenues generated by our athletes at the Olympic Games are directly returned to those who make the Games the global spectacle that it is,\\\" World Athletics president Sebastian Coe said in a statement.\", \"from\": 530, \"to\": 807, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 747, \"end\": 762, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999340616, \"rank\": 6.576239556190523e-11, \"text\": \"World Athletics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_