/resource/Student_athlete_compensation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.639370450880351e-32, \"text\": \"NIL\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Student_athlete_compensation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Student_athlete_compensation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the age\", \"from\": 3367, \"to\": 3374}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That point is even more poignant in an age of NIL marked by pseudo-salaries paid by booster-backed collectives.\", \"from\": 3385, \"to\": 3496, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3431, \"end\": 3434, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Student_athlete_compensation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.639370450880351e-32, \"text\": \"NIL\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Student_athlete_compensation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Student_athlete_compensation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That point\", \"from\": 3385, \"to\": 3395}, {\"ngram\": \"even more poignant\", \"from\": 3399, \"to\": 3417}, {\"ngram\": \"an age\", \"from\": 3421, \"to\": 3427}, {\"ngram\": \"pseudo\", \"from\": 3445, \"to\": 3451}, {\"ngram\": \"salaries\", \"from\": 3452, \"to\": 3460}, {\"ngram\": \"booster-backed collectives\", \"from\": 3469, \"to\": 3495}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those NIL deals effectively allow donors to pay athletes to play at a specific school - a nonsensical workaround in a status quo in which schools and conferences cannot directly pay athletes.\", \"from\": 3497, \"to\": 3688, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3503, \"end\": 3506, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Student_athlete_compensation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.639370450880351e-32, \"text\": \"NIL\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Student_athlete_compensation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Student_athlete_compensation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"donors\", \"from\": 3531, \"to\": 3537}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 3545, \"to\": 3553}, {\"ngram\": \"a 